    <detaileddescription>
<para>Fluent C++ builder for <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_description" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphDescription</ref>. Mirrors Tryll::Client::GraphDescription from client-cpp. Not a USTRUCT — for programmatic C++ use only.</para>
<para>Example: <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_description" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphDescription</ref> Graph = <ref refid="struct_f_tryll_graph_builder" kindref="compound">FTryllGraphBuilder()</ref> .AddNode(TEXT(&quot;gen&quot;), ETryllNodeType::Generate, {{TEXT(&quot;model_name&quot;), TEXT(&quot;mymodel&quot;)}}) .Wire(TEXT(&quot;gen&quot;), TEXT(&quot;done&quot;), TEXT(&quot;END&quot;)) .SetStartNode(TEXT(&quot;gen&quot;)) .SetDefaultModelName(TEXT(&quot;mymodel&quot;)) .Build(); </para>
